<div class="sect1">
<div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both">
<a name="resolutions"></a>Resolutions</h2></div></div></div>


<p>
The NetBSD Foundation has passed the following resolutions:
</p>

<div class="itemizedlist"><ul class="itemizedlist" style="list-style-type: disc; ">
<li class="listitem">
<a class="ulink" href="resolutions/20030114-administration-exec.txt" target="_top">
Formation of administration-exec@NetBSD.org</a>.
(2003/01/14, amended 2003/03/11)
</li>
<li class="listitem">
<a class="ulink" href="resolutions/20030114-communication-exec.txt" target="_top">
Formation of communication-exec@NetBSD.org</a>.
(2003/01/14, amended 2003/03/11)
</li>
<li class="listitem">
<a class="ulink" href="resolutions/20030114-finance-exec.txt" target="_top">
Formation of finance-exec@NetBSD.org</a>.
(2003/01/14, amended 2003/03/11)
</li>
<li class="listitem">
<a class="ulink" href="resolutions/20030114-membership-exec.txt" target="_top">
Formation of membership-exec@NetBSD.org</a>.
(2003/01/14, amended 2003/03/11)
</li>
<li class="listitem">
<a class="ulink" href="resolutions/20030114-technical-exec.txt" target="_top">
Formation of technical-exec@NetBSD.org</a>.
(2003/01/14, amended 2003/03/11)
</li>
<li class="listitem">
<a class="ulink" href="resolutions/20030923-core.txt" target="_top">
Formation of core@NetBSD.org</a>.
(2003/09/23)
</li>
<li class="listitem">
<a class="ulink" href="resolutions/20031202-pkgsrc-pmc.txt" target="_top">
Formation of pkgsrc-pmc@NetBSD.org</a>.
(2003/12/02)
</li>
<li class="listitem">
<a class="ulink" href="resolutions/20041006-www-pmc.txt" target="_top">
Formation of www-pmc@NetBSD.org</a>.
(2004/10/06)
</li>
</ul></div>

<p>
The administration-exec, communication-exec and technical-exec
Executive Committees do not exist anymore.</p>
</div>
